OL,7,FOn her second day of giving evidence
OL,8,Fto the Horizon IT scandal inquiry, Ms
OL,9,FVan Den Bogerd was asked about the
OL,10,Fcases of several individual sub-
OL,11,Fpostmasters and their branches.
OL,13,FThe inquiry was shown a series of
OL,14,Fletters and emails concerning the case
OL,15,Fof the late Martin Griffiths, who was
OL,16,Fsacked from his Post Office branch in
OL,17,F2013, and hounded for #100,000 worth
OL,18,Fof losses - which did not exist.
