OL,7,FMr Griffiths, who'd worked for the
OL,8,FPost Office for 18 years, took his own
OL,9,Flife after he had been deemed culpable
OL,10,Ffor an armed robbery at his branch in
OL,11,FMay of that year.
OL,13,FMs Van Den Bogerd was shown a letter
OL,14,Fblaming the Post Office solely for his
OL,15,Fsuicide and she was accused of
OL,16,Fpressuring his widow to accept a
OL,17,Fpayout in return for her silence.
OL,19,FIt comes after she yesterday claimed
OL,20,Fshe had forgotten about .
