OL,7,FMr Griffiths attempted to take his own
OL,8,Flife on September 23, 2013 and
OL,9,Fremained in a coma for three weeks in
OL,10,Fhospital. On October 11, his life
OL,11,Fsupport machine was switched off and
OL,12,Fhe died. A coroner later concluded he
OL,13,Fdied by suicide.
OL,15,FMs Van Den Bogerd said Mr Griffith's
OL,16,Fcase was "tragic" and says she was
OL,17,F"concerned for the family" after his
OL,18,Fdeath.
