OL,7,FAfter learning of Mr Griffith's
OL,8,Fsuicide attempt, Post Office staff
OL,9,Fsuggested in an email chain - which
OL,10,Fwas forwarded to Ms Van Den Bogerd -
OL,11,Fthat they hire a specialist media
OL,12,Flawyer.
OL,14,FMr Beer pressed Ms Van Den Bogerd over
OL,15,Fthe culture of the post office and
OL,16,Fquestioned why their first thought on
OL,17,Freceiving that news was they need a
OL,18,Fmedia lawyer, rather than supporting
OL,19,Fthe family.
